1. 挂载U盘安装python
1>格式化U盘   mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda2
2> 挂载到 /mnt/usb 目录下   
修改 /etc/profile 
export PATH=/usr/bin:/usr/sbin:/bin:/sbin:/mnt/usb/usr/bin:/mnt/usb/sbin:/mnt/usb/usr/local/bin:/mnt/usb/usr/local/sbin
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/mnt/usb/usr/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
修改/etc/opkg.conf
dest root /
dest ram /tmp
lists_dir ext /var/opkg-lists
option overlay_root /overlay
dest usb /mnt/usb
3> 
opkg update   
opkg -d usb install python

2. 将网关程序考到板子上  scp -r wot_gateway/ root@192.168.8.1:/mnt/usb/
3. 运行与平台通信的程序  python  /mnt/usb/wot_gateway/bin/gateway/main.py
4.  运行alljoyn后台   /mnt/usb/wot_gateway/bin/alljoyn/alljoyn-daemon &
5. 运行alljoyn 服务端   /mnt/usb/wot_gateway/bin/alljoyn/aj_server 127.0.0.1
​6. 运行 microduino     /mnt/usb/wot_gateway/bin/microduino/helloworld
